title: 'Value for money'
body: 'Best in this price range. I am using safari luggage since last 10 years'

title: 'Defected product'
body: 'The media could not be loaded. Side Rubber not fitted properly nylon threads flittering from sides poor finishing.'

title: 'Mast Hai'
body: 'Superb Purchasing by me. Value for money'

title: 'Cheap stuff'
body: 'The cheapness of the product is quite visible. Is t much scratch resistant. Zips give away easily.'

title: 'Spacious and sturdy'
body: 'Love this bag.. very useful for long travels..it’s very strong and the color is elegant. Go for it.. bought it in DEAL'

title: 'Value for money'
body: 'Got quality bag in affordable price . Colour is a described in photo. But there was black decorative part missing in one wheel'

title: 'I’ve bought it to gift on engagement'
body: 'Product looks premium and has 5 years of international warranty and colour is the centre of all the talks. I am satisfied with the product.'
